Class LegAF

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.magknight.route.Leg
      • com.magknight.route.proc.legs.LegAF
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LegParser<LegAF>

    public class LegAF
extends Leg
implements LegParser<LegAF>
    AF leg defines a track over ground at a specified constant distance from a database DME navaid For more information. See ARINC database documentation.
    Since:
    5/19/2020
    Author:
    Cian Mc Sweeney
